1 buy 1 ward and 1 sentry ward
2 give 1 ward to ally hero
3 make the ally hero lock cpmbining the ward
4 give 1 sentry ward to ally hero
5 make the ally hero unlock the ward
6 Double click to switch between ward and sentry
7 you will have 2 wards 1 sentry
8 Repeat the process to get an infinite number of wards
